Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â When they were alone in the darkness, she felt the strange, licentiousness of him hovering upon her. She was troubled and repelled. Why should he turn like this?

Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â ''What is it?'' she asked in dread.

